  <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
  <h6>Is League Draft secure?</h6>
  <p>You may notice the URL does not start with https, so...not as secure as it could be.  
  However, Payments are done through trusted vendors in a way that no personal data is passed to my servers or stored (only email address) so I think I have done a good job protecting you here.</p>
  <li>Once active, Dwolla payments will redirect to Dwolla which uses SSL, so it's very secure</li>
  <li>Stripe payments use encryption keys and they build a client-side token which gets sent to me to send to Stripe for payment verification</li> 

